channel.title: Galaxyx 718
channel.description:
Galaxy X is a new RSPS released 8/09/2015. We are extremely excited to be up and running on our new VPS. Come join a new amazing community at Galaxy X! All skills are working, 120 capes, custom mini games, custom items, and when the server grows if the majority of the players want, we have the ability to upgrade the max combat level to 169 and all skills go to level 120!! Come be a member of the next best RSPS. The server is built for the players, if you want something in game and get support behind you, we will add it!
http://galaxyx718.com/
